title: Cartoon Donald Trump's Bedtime Routine May Give You Nightmares
text:
Cartoon Donald Trump's Bedtime Routine May Give You Nightmares Sleep well, Mr. President!   President Donald Trump’s pre-sleep rituals have received a cartoon makeover. The “ Late Show ” imagined on Friday what POTUS does before drifting off inside the White House each night. Just don’t let it give you nightmares.
